    public static final class AssociationHandle.InboundPayload
extends java.lang.Object
implements AssociationHandle.HandleEvent, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Message sent to the listener registered to an association (via the Promise returned by AssociationHandle.readHandlerPromise()) when an inbound payload arrives.

    param: payload The raw bytes that were sent by the remote endpoint.
